other_title: デジモンアドベンチャー tri. 第5章「共生」 (Japanese)
plot: The countdown begins to the destruction of the real world at the hands of the out-of-control Meicoomon. Meicoomon's partner Meiko Mochizuki worries that this Digimon is one that should never have been created. Omegamon, Hackmon's ultimate form Jesmon, Alphamon, and the Digimon apparently mutated by Meicoomon face off in battle.
ending_theme: "Ai Kotoba" (アイコトバ) by Ayumi Miyazaki & AiM
